MidiRenderer 3.3.0.0 + Repack MidiRenderer - a program for rendering MIDI, you can easily convert this format to such formats as WAV, MP3, OGG, FLAC, APE, AMR or WMA. Often this software is used by people if you want to play a MIDI file on a portable player, in a car, or if you want to record MIDI on an Audio disc. The difference from the alternatives is that you get a direct MIDI-rendering without using a sound card.
